{"tid":2344780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：聯合相同理念國家與中國抗衡","createTime":"2020-12-29T04:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T11:16:07.000Z","uid":278587,"like":10,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"488b19ea0ab20649a32e002aacb05fbd739fd350","tid":2344780,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567564-20201229.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567564-20201229.htm&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8734f6cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567564-20201229.htm&h=bc882f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567564-20201229.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人拜登指出，面對當今最艱鉅的威脅需要美國的參與及領導，但若只得美國單打獨鬥也無法解決任何威脅。<br />\n<br />\n拜登強調，在與中國競爭，並在貿易、科技、人權等追究北京責任的問題上，若聯合理念相近夥伴捍衛共同利益及價值，將能夠令美國處於更強而有力的位置。<br />\n<br />\n拜登指出，單是美國只佔全球經濟25%，但若與民主夥伴站在一起，經濟談判籌碼將倍增。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，在美中關係的議題上，不論是推動外交政策，保護美國勞工和智識產權等的計劃，抑或是確保印太區域的安全與繁榮、捍衛人權等，聯合有相同願景的國家，將更能有效達成目標。"},{"pid":"33671c540b8c90ca3ac7728742d6e3b1a0a51953","tid":2344780,"uid":186,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平平又輸啦"},{"pid":"b6a9b5e621cb81b526e40d88c32e1ffddfe22d83","tid":2344780,"uid":253016,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"睇黎有人教路<br />\n最岩全球撚心意<br />\n繼續嘴炮反支 繼續魚肉14億支那人"},{"pid":"38313a7dae6df6c9a4b8ac746db3528c12413122","tid":2344780,"uid":37719,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"拜登藍絲黎，還我trump!"},{"pid":"56e051117ace6e965eae551858f2c6a98cb97b3f","tid":2344780,"uid":130105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"中國又搭到eu, 又攪到個個R乜乜經濟圈，